            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "This character\u2019s hands tremble like leaves in a storm, making it impossible to draw a bowstring steady or toss a stone on target. They\u2019ve accidentally pelted a friend with a wild throw more than once, earning wary glances. At the village fair, their darts land in the dirt\u2014or someone\u2019s hat. Precision is a cruel joke to them.",
